Entries.default: "You are very lucky to be so favored by the queen."
"Will the fountains ever be as they were? I miss them."
"Long life to our queen! She treats us well."
"Forgive me, I have much to finish before the day is through."
"That is a fine bird. Have you come for Hylea's blessing?"
"You are very kind, to speak on our behalf."
"Will we all see Ukaizo? Perhaps if the queen takes her household..."
"There must be many fine palaces, where you are from."
